{
  "stem": "20848.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You sold it to people who had bread and food, like the [GERMAN] and the-- and the kapos, and people who were influential prisoners, halflings.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I used to smuggle out the clothing every single day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I used to bribe the [GERMAN] in a block not to send my mother to [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then I got her a job in a [GERMAN], which was a sewing-- a sewing place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I always-- I looked after my mother because the luck for survival was coming through me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I looked after her, not she after me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you understand?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- we had food to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were very lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because-- because I was smuggling the things out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day, I was caught smuggling it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she threw me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Who threw you out?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The kapo.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schmidt.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She threw me out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now, my-- my-- all my trouble started, because now I wasn't anymore protected from selections.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a big selection in the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother-- naked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we block by block had to go to selection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mengele was the one that was making the selection.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And again, they put on one side the people to live and on the other side the people to die.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And again, my mother was put on the side to live, and I was put-- my number was taken down on the side to die, because I was a child.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I return to my barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And again, this is a third time I went to the-- to the wire to tell Chaim Kaminski that I have been-- my number has been taken down to go to the gas chambers in the selection.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he said to me, don't you worry, he said to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
